            <abstract id="ref3" label="Abstract">Communications Workers of America, Local 1250 represented AT&amp;T Long Lines employees in Connecticut. The Local was active from the early 1960s until 2000, when its membership was absorbed by CWA Local 1153 based in Westchester, NY. The collection consists of minutes of Executive Board and General Membership meetings, bargaining files, grievance records, reports, correspondence, and photographs.</abstract>
