        <processinfo id="ref45">
            <head>Processing Information</head>
            <p>Photographs and certificates were separated from this collection during processing and were established as a separate collection, the Communications Workers of America, Local 1250 Photograph Collections (PHOTOS 230). In 2013, the photograph and certificate collection was reincorporated into the Communications Workers of America, Local 1250 (WAG 258).</p>
        </processinfo>
